  ('Biology (B.Sc.)', '20%', 'Locally restricted admission (NC); German C1-C2 required (DSH-2 or TestDaF 4x4); strong natural sciences background required; laboratory and fieldwork components from first semester; research-oriented program; Göttingen is strong in ecology, evolutionary biology, and molecular biology', 35, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2.0, 'AAA', 35, NULL, NULL, NULL),
