  ('Agricultural Sciences (B.Sc.)', '30%', 'Admission-free (no NC); German C1-C2 required (DSH-2 or TestDaF 4x4); Göttingen''s faculty of agricultural sciences is internationally top-ranked; covers crop science, animal science, agribusiness; fieldwork components included; apply via uni-assist portal', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2.5, 'ABB', 33, NULL, NULL, NULL),
